title: How to draw figure of normal fan
body:
As README.md says, "The result will be saved in test_seq/tRNA/c.diphtheriae_tRNA.rnapoly, which can be read directly or used with rna_poly.py to produce a Sage polytope for further investigation.", I could get .rnapoly file by executing `pmfe-parametlizer`, however, I don't see how to use this file with rna_poly.py module to draw figures shown in your paper. 
Could you tell me how to use these in more detail?
